<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sucesso - WhatsCalendar</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #00E676;
            --primary-dark: #00C853;
            --accent: #2979FF;
            --bg: #F4F7FE;
            --text-dark: #2B3674;
            --text-gray: #A3AED0;
            --card-bg: #FFFFFF;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #F4F7FE 0%, #E2EDF8 100%);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .container {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 50px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(112, 144, 176, 0.12);
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--primary);
        }

        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.1);
            color: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            margin: 0 auto 25px auto;
        }

        h2 { 
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p { 
            color: var(--text-dark); 
            font-size: 15px; 
            margin-bottom: 15px; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #F4F7FE;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .info-label {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
        <h2>Conectado com Sucesso!</h2>
        <p>O seu WhatsApp foi vinculado às suas agendas do Google com sucesso.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">WhatsApp:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= whatsappNumber %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">Horário de Envio:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= preferredTime %></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 25px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-gray);">
            Você receberá sua agenda todos os dias no horário configurado.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
